oji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>揾唔番篇文啦<br />\n<br />\n大致係話英國一個郡都係叫country<br />\n<br />\n一國兩制講國家,應該叫nation</blockquote><br />\n郡係叫County 唔係叫country <br />\n至於用nation係要強調個民族一致性</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n柒左自<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之佢篇文大概係講state,country, nation係唔同意思，咁上下</blockquote><br />\nstate=強調政權 政府<br />\nnation=強調民族<br />\ncountry=相對中性 單純指國家"},{"pid":"0051634895935239a1cfa55a81de276087f8fa13","tid":507172,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T11:19:49.000Z","msg":"Nationalism=民族主義<br />\n所以你會估到Nation同民族，身份認同有關<br />\n而理解State 你可以參考美國 United States<br />\n特色係咩呢？係聯邦政府 由一大堆state組成<br />\n所以你會發現每個state嘅法例唔同 有啲地方可以食大麻 揸槍<br />\n所以state係同個政府 政權個關係大啲<br />\n形容美國係一個country 但唔係一個state<br />\n所以19話一國兩制用nation係貼切啲 但country未至於錯<br />\n<br />\n而樓主講 中國話台灣係一個small country就明顯係錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60652beee256f715b4f6fe2fa9132f9ee34d2b66","tid":507172,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T11:24:36.000Z","msg":"country = 鄉土<br />\nstate = 有法人身份既國家<br />\nnation = 民族國家"},{"pid":"8cddd72f5bc47ef71661b7c7984e9bedf94bb1ab","tid":507172,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T11:29:29.000Z","msg":"sovereign state"}]}